        "subject": "=Nueva integracion TPV - {{ $('Detectar TPV no integrado').first().json.tpvNombre }}",
        "html": "=<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#f1f1f1;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;\">\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background:#f1f1f1;padding:32px 16px;\">\n  <tr><td align=\"center\">\n    <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"max-width:560px;\">\n      <tr><td style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#111111,#2d0c0c);border-radius:14px 14px 0 0;padding:28px 32px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#fca5a5;\">Yurest · Integraciones</p>\n        <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;\">Nueva integración TPV pendiente</p>\n      </td></tr>\n      <tr><td style=\"background:#ffffff;padding:28px 32px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.6;\">\n          Se ha añadido un cliente con una integración TPV <strong>no realizada</strong>. Se ha creado la tarea correspondiente en el proyecto <strong>Integraciones</strong> de Asana.\n        </p>\n        <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border:1.5px solid #f1f5f9;border-radius:10px;margin:0 0 18px;\">\n          <tr><td style=\"background:#f8fafc;padding:10px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#fc5858;\">Datos de referencia</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;font-size:13px;color:#1e293b;line-height:1.7;\">\n            <strong>TPV:</strong> {{ $('Detectar TPV no integrado').first().json.tpvNombre }}<br>\n            <strong>Cliente (nombre comercial):</strong> {{ $('Detectar TPV no integrado').first().json.nombreCom }}<br>\n            <strong>Comercial responsable:</strong> {{ $('Detectar TPV no integrado').first().json.comercial }}<br>\n            <strong>Persona de referencia del TPV:</strong> {{ $('Detectar TPV no integrado').first().json.tpvPersona || '—' }}<br>\n            <strong>Email de referencia del TPV:</strong> {{ $('Detectar TPV no integrado').first().json.tpvEmail || '—' }}\n          </td></tr>\n        </table>\n        <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;\">Equipo Yurest</p>\n      </td></tr>\n      <tr><td style=\"background:#f8fafc;border-radius:0 0 14px 14px;border-top:1.5px solid #e2e8f0;padding:14px 32px;font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;\">© Yurest · Aviso automático</td></tr>\n    </table>\n  </td></tr>\n</table>\n</body>\n</html>",
